# SHACL spec §4.1.3 — sh:nodeKind data graph (NodeKindExampleShape).
# Source: https://www.w3.org/TR/shacl/#NodeKindConstraintComponent
# Objects of ex:knows are the target nodes (sh:targetObjectsOf).
# ex:Bob ex:knows ex:Alice — ex:Alice is an IRI → conforms.
# ex:Alice ex:knows "Bob"  — "Bob" is a literal, not an IRI → 1 violation.
PREFIX ex: <http://example.com/ns#>

ex:Bob ex:knows ex:Alice .
ex:Alice ex:knows "Bob" .
